<glossary>
<definition id="fs-id1170902349147">
<term>fringes</term>
<meaning id="fs-id1170904155828">bright and dark patterns of interference</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-id1170904118034">
<term>order</term>
<meaning id="fs-id1170902163135">integer <emphasis effect="italics">m</emphasis> used in the equations for constructive and destructive interference for a double slit</meaning>
</definition>
